<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="<%= language === 'zh' ? 'zh-TW' : 'en' %>">
<head>
<!-- meta attributes -->
<meta charset="utf-8">
<meta name="author" content="Jack Gowan">
<meta name="description" content="first built maze">
<title>The Maze - Through the Traps</title>
<link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/a_maze_style.css">
</head>
<body>
<h1 class="main-title"><%= translations?.[language]?.title || 'The Chamber of Six' %></h1>

  <div class="room-container">
    <div class="content-wrapper">
      <div class="room-image">
        <img src="/images/a4_trap-5-roku_lair.png" alt="Chamber with drawn bows">
      </div>
      <div class="room-content">
        <div class="room-text">
          <code>
            <%- translations?.[language]?.text || `<p>You enter a vast chamber. The walls are lined with hundreds of drawn bows, arrows nocked and aimed at six stone panels in the center of the room.</p>
            <p>Each panel bears a number: 1, 2, 3, 4, 5, and 6.</p>
            <p>Above the panels, an inscription glows with an eerie light:</p>
            <br>
            <p><em>"Six paths before thee, five bring thy end.</em></p>
            <p><em>One path of hot death in a foreign land of grapevines</em></p>
            <p><em>One path of laughter in a foreign land of smiles</em></p>
            <p><em>One path of clear death in a foreign land of hotsprings</em></p>
            <p><em>One path of still death in a foreign land of stables</em></p>
            <p><em>One path of sibling death in a foreign land of pasta</em></p>
            <p><em>One path of death in the foreign land of stone</em></p>
            <br>
            <p>Your hand trembles as you approach. One wrong choice means death by a thousand arrows.</p>` %>
          </code>
        </div>

        <div class="navigation">
          <p><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.prompt || 'Which panel do you press?' %></p>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-6-sanjyu-golden-room-2"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[0] || 'Press Panel 1' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-6-sanjyu-golden-room-2"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[1] || 'Press Panel 2' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-6-sanjyu-golden-room-2"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[2] || 'Press Panel 3' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-6-sanjyu-golden-room-2"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[3] || 'Press Panel 4' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-6-sanjyu-golden-room-1"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[4] || 'Press Panel 5' %></a>
          <a href="/maze/dark-trap-6-sanjyu-golden-room-2"><%= translations?.[language]?.choices?.options?.[5] || 'Press Panel 6' %></a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
